Py9 Library

Simple library providing client and server utilities for 9P2000
protocol. Check `src/py9/exmaples/fileserver.py` for server example or
run it with `python3 -m py9.examples.fileserver 0.0.0.0 5555 ./`.

Check [llmfs](https://github.com/fish4terrisa-MSDSM/llmfs) for example in reallife usage.

Forked from [~emru/py9](https://git.sr.ht/~emru/py9)
